#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.152"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.152:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.152:0.2"
msgid "15. Navapurāṇavagga "
msgstr "15. The Old and the New "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 152. Kimatthiyabrahmacariyasutta → kimatthiyasuttaṃ (bj) | kimatthiya (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.152:0.3"
msgid "152. Kimatthiyabrahmacariyasutta "
msgstr "152. What’s the Purpose of the Spiritual Life? "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.152:1.1"
msgid "“Sace vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow another path were to ask you: "

msgctxt "sn35.152:1.2"
msgid "‘kimatthiyaṃ, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti? "
msgstr "‘Reverends, what’s the purpose of living the spiritual life with the ascetic Gotama?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.152:1.3"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha: "
msgstr "You should answer them: "

msgctxt "sn35.152:1.4"
msgid "‘dukkhassa kho, āvuso, pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti. "
msgstr "‘The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely understand suffering.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.152:1.5"
msgid "Sace pana vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "If wanderers who follow other paths were to ask you: "

msgctxt "sn35.152:1.6"
msgid "‘katamaṃ panāvuso, dukkhaṃ, yassa pariññāya samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti? "
msgstr "‘Reverends, what is that suffering?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.152:1.7"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha: "
msgstr "You should answer them: "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.152:2.1"
msgid "‘Cakkhu kho, āvuso, dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "‘The eye is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.2"
msgid "tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely understand this. "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.3"
msgid "Rūpā dukkhā; "
msgstr "Sights … "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.4"
msgid "tesaṃ pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.5"
msgid "Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "Eye consciousness … "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.6"
msgid "tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.7"
msgid "Cakkhusamphasso dukkho; "
msgstr "Eye contact … "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.8"
msgid "tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.9"
msgid "Yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by eye contact is also suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.10"
msgid "tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati … pe … "
msgstr "The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely understand this. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.152:2.11"
msgid "jivhā dukkhā … "
msgstr "The ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.12"
msgid "mano dukkho; "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.13"
msgid "tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.14"
msgid "yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact is also suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.15"
msgid "tassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely understand this. "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.16"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, āvuso, dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "This is that suffering. "

msgctxt "sn35.152:2.17"
msgid "yassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti. "
msgstr "The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to completely understand this.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.152:2.18"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyāthā”ti. "
msgstr "When questioned by wanderers who follow other paths, that’s how you should answer them.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.152:2.19"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

